3.1
--
* Data.Conduit.Async - fix possible threads leak. Add documentation.

3.0
---
* Data.Conduit.mergeSources - fixed bug when input Sources were not
closed when outgoing source is closed.

2.3
---
* Data.Conduit.Utils is introduced. It's possible to use it to create
(source,sink) pairs.

2.2
---
* Changed the sink* family. Now it takes additional boolean argument that
specifies if channel should be closed. Old behavior can be archived by
using 'True'.

* Documentation improved.
